{"tid":2488971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"數臭老細 入黎放抵怨氣","createTime":"2021-04-14T15:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:23:21.000Z","uid":339908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbd7bfa04f8529a0b48aa556e5bc0a41897bace","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">背景</span>：絲 幼教工作 已離職<br />\n<br />\n老細 過左退休年齡 仲賴死唔走 <br />\n係到教壞下一代 （藍屍教育）<br />\n<br />\n下面兩主任為左搏上位 搞9啲老師 <br />\n鐘意分化，分派系 <br />\n好地地教書唔撚得既，日日搞到啲老師勾心鬥角，<br />\n你討好邊個主任，個主任就會咩都幫你頂<br />\n你唔幫個主任上位呢，就日日玩到你殘。<br />\n工作量會多到核爆，日日做到 11-12點<br />\n<br />\n唔單只對老師下屬係咁 ，但最仆街既係，<br />\n老細同兩隻鬥牛仲要針對埋小朋友。<br />\n只要主任A 鐘意既小朋友，另一位主任B 就會針對個個小朋友，<br />\n一定要鬧到小朋友喊 佢先認為 &quot; 教導 &quot; 成功！<br />\nOh, confound it!<br />\n5"},{"pid":"99ea276b46a2709808eb70729bf531af11ae3d09","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97bf8ea4a8e4b66c2e7df87229d3558dc4107e61","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62686330637706ba45b88affd0ff331ee0a21850","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b57259bf251c8d5ad207587d6e9b03c1217bf110","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9385d5b7ae91dc4c9b1d5dd6ed71ea8a3abe4dc8","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac1be2995ced0b50f0306333425d00b43cad4290","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb34c7d0ac4196acdc9a0ac700fc64e0b60e45dd","tid":2488971,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcae2c06